            .grp_icon  
            %p Invite a friend to enrol - receive discounts for you and your friend
      %ul.terms_policy_links.aos-item.aos-init.aos-animate{"data-aos" => "fade-up", "data-aos-duration" => "1500"}
        %li
          %h4
